						<summary>

						<p>On a pillar of the <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa</hi> in front of the temple of Sūrēśvara.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1751, Virōdhi, Āśvija śu. 13 = 1829 A.D., October 10.</hi></p>						

						<p>It states that Bōḍi Kṛishṭayya set up a <hi rend="italic">dhvaja-staṁbha</hi> on the abovedate and fixed it with mortar in the month of Phāguṇa. </p>						

